{"type": "article", "id": 26602, "title": "这个丹麦家具推出的副牌，产品是200多种很美的文具", "description": "“个性比之前受到了更多的关注”。\r\n", "date": "2016-05-10T06:53:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27409, "name": "丹麦家具品牌"}, {"id": 3208, "name": "Normann Copenhagen"}, {"id": 27410, "name": "Daily Fiction"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 465, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703122459NHr2IvfEL9QtV58b.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>丹麦家具品牌<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/journal/products/daily-fiction?utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=Introducing%20the%20Daily%20Fiction%20collection%20-%20a%20new%20design%20collaboration%20with%20Femmes%20Rgionales&amp;utm_content=Introducing%20the%20Daily%20Fiction%20collection%20-%20a%20new%20design%20collaboration%20with%20Femmes%20Rgionales%20CID_26fa83b9a0d22d4bce2500fac111c521&amp;utm_source=Email%20marketing%20software&amp;utm_term=See%20more\"> Normann Copenhagen </a>近期发展出了它的副牌 Daily Fiction，有超过 200 种（包括不同型号和 18 种颜色）小型文具。铅笔、笔记本、橡皮擦、卷笔刀等文具大多在最熟悉的形状中，但已换上了不同材料和颜色，有纯净素雅的纯色条纹，也有像大理石砖一样的不规则圆点纹，兼具古典优雅和粗旷现代的风格。设计者想以此鼓励人们选择到最适合自己风格的文具。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122446MCz9w2mVsOg453ko.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122447WDnqxhLJCTpj9wQy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031224470fLlPqOi4eZ2CAtb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122448sdNxQG1tgIPiYw3M.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122448e8o2YMENULuKRVcp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122449UOzLCWwg6RHkYn5t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>Normann Copenhagen 在中国的推广代表莫钧元告诉《好奇心日报》， “Daily Fiction 的风格是 bold（陡峭的、醒目的、大胆的），从颜色到材料都会比较纯净或者锐利”。这个品牌将针对 15 到 30 岁的消费者，比起通常家具品牌定位在 20 岁到 45 岁来说更年轻。“在成年之后，小时候的乐趣就丧失了，可以重新找回小时候的幻想。”</p>\n<p>Daily Fiction 系列选择了帆布、天鹅绒、金属、塑料、纸等多种材料。定价在中高端，小型硬壳笔记本 129 元、圆珠笔和三角尺子 99 元，接近快时尚概念下衣服的价格。在更新上也会比家具更快，到明年初将发布第二批。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122449Wrsv7kbRHI4duMKw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122450aoZN5YAsyHUOb2qS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031224502qUf4MnIwe5uQg9a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>Daily Fiction 的概念由品牌管理者 Britt Bonnesen 推出，她曾经在时尚行业工作，也使得这个品牌拥有更强烈的快时尚特征，“在做 Normann Copenhagen 时我们获得了很多关于时尚的启发，而很长一段时间里，我们都想增加一个关于小物件的新的分类。”他们选择了哥本哈根当地一家时尚资讯公司 Femmes Regionales 负责规划产品生产线而不是产品设计公司，设计者来自原有团队。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122451uS7vNYp8crsgDJol.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.21388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Britt Bonnesen （中间）</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>重视小型物品的设计是不少设计品牌近期发展的方向，而近期发展迅速的 HAY 也有更大比例的配件设计，他们在不少店中设立与快闪店概念类似的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/19432.html\"> Mini Market </a>放文具等小件。</p>\n<p>莫钧元并不否认对 HAY 的借鉴，他认为以文具这类小物品为相同出发点是“想覆盖到年轻的人群，大概 20 出头可能还不需要买家具的人，让品牌和个人先建立起联系。”但在明年上市的产品中会扩展更多更细腻的产品线。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122451xq8b6pasWvIfMOYm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Daily Fiction 在丹麦哥本哈根的展示空间 </div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>此前，Normann Copenhagen 在米兰设计周上发布了一组可进行扁平化包装的沙发，定位住在大城市里的年轻人。这种非常利于运输的形式从宜家发展出来已获得了不少家具品牌的接受。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122452w38JNtE4LPBvzxlC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>Normann Copenhagen 即将于今年 8 月底在上海设立亚洲第一家旗舰店，届时将推出 Daily Fiction 系列，比东京、首尔等地推出的时间更早。Normann Copenhagen 在中国目前的销售方式是线上和买手店，Daily Fiction 并不加入这些销售渠道。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122452RMqA3gP5kbzrNv6y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122453sf3WFRQ84v1PjxD7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122453RvgraozEMUCkmLGZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122455MoxqvWOy9hzpE1XD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122455p0mHOjhaUtCxNX4n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122455jNCiDwdH0yfEe4zZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031224569DJiQ50Onc1X7Cws.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122456GpYfleEQzs3vFwLi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122457WEUzHls58JOhd1jC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122458RbVzJ85iWNQFUmGo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031224580iJyEL1gSIYQZz7j.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/04/29/normann-copenhagen-launch-daily-fiction-range-accessories-stationery-fashion-design/\">dezeen</a>、<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/journal/products/daily-fiction?utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=Introducing%20the%20Daily%20Fiction%20collection%20-%20a%20new%20design%20collaboration%20with%20Femmes%20Rgionales&amp;utm_content=Introducing%20the%20Daily%20Fiction%20collection%20-%20a%20new%20design%20collaboration%20with%20Femmes%20Rgionales%20CID_26fa83b9a0d22d4bce2500fac111c521&amp;utm_source=Email%20marketing%20software&amp;utm_term=See%20more\">Normann Copenhagen</a><a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/journal/products/daily-fiction?utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=Introducing%20the%20Daily%20Fiction%20collection%20-%20a%20new%20design%20collaboration%20with%20Femmes%20Rgionales&amp;utm_content=Introducing%20the%20Daily%20Fiction%20collection%20-%20a%20new%20design%20collaboration%20with%20Femmes%20Rgionales%20CID_26fa83b9a0d22d4bce2500fac111c521&amp;utm_source=Email%20marketing%20software&amp;utm_term=See%20more\"> </a></p>\n\n"}